<p>I was keen to use a rapid process on this project and thankfully Fergus was willing to let me lead and trusted me to deliver a site that would work and be easy to manage.</p>

<p>Fergus was very keen to keep the maroon colour which initially I wasnâ€™t sure about but by balancing it with a healthy amount of white space it works well.</p>

